Table 18. Supplemental data for state governments

Note: Local government data are estimates subject to variability. Population figures are from the Bureau of the Census, Table 1. Annual Estimates of the Resident Population for the United States, Regions, States, and Puerto Rico: April 1, 2010 to July 1, 2018 (NST-EST2018-01), December 2018.
a/"Personal income" is from the U.S. Department of Commerce, Survey of Current Business, September 2018.
b/"Total general expenditure" excludes utilities, state-operated liquor stores, and insurance trust benefits.
c/"General functions only" FTE excludes utilities, and state-operated liquor stores.
